title: Demi Rose goes NAKED as she enjoys Valentine's bubble bath | Daily Mail Online
text: Share this article Share With her hair piled high on her head and a face full of make-up, she blew the bubbles seductively at the camera for the video. Meanwhile she is reportedly planning to relocate to LA- home to former flame Tyga and Kylie Jenner. Nude ambition: The 21-year-old Instagram model showed off the talent that won her 3.8 million Instagram followers, by posing completely naked from her petal-filled bathtub Poser: With her hair piled high on her head and a face full of make-up, she blew the bubbles seductively at the camera for the video A source told MailOnline: 'Brummy Demi is planning a move to the US as she has set her sights on Hollywood. 'She is already trained in acting as she attended theatre school as a child. She has become friends with Michael Bay, who discovered Megan Fox. 'Maybe he will give Demi her big break.' Not so solo? Demi shared a snap of a bouquet of red roses on Valentine's Former flame? The social media favourite became the talk of the globe last summer after being pictured with Tyga on several occasions A source told MailOnline: 'Brummy Demi is planning a move to the US as she has set her sights on Hollywood' On Thursday evening, the DJ-in-training posted a low-key photo of herself giving a thumbs up, writing: 'Hi babies.' The social media favourite became the talk of the globe last summer after being pictured with Tyga on several occasions, including during a trip to the Cannes Film Festival. But things moved on at a whirlwind pace after the Ayo hitmaker got back together with his ex Kylie Jenner, with the pair even sparking engagement rumours after she showcased a giant diamond on her ring finger on social media. Familiar: Demi looks rather like Tyga's current love Kylie Jenner who he has been dating on and off for a couple of years (pictured) Following her sudden rise to fame, Demi's parents Barrie, 78, a former bank manager, and Christine, 61, said she is a very different person at home and insisted they were proud of her. Her mother said: 'We're right behind her. She's such a beautiful girl, why shouldn't she? If you've got it, flaunt it. 'She's very kind and a really down-to-earth girl â€“ nothing like what we are seeing in the press.'
